<2a94d88a63985c1bd5dd8459da37d19bShape> sh:property <e199f7d9a28f6ce2fd661a99af5e8000dateShape>;
    sh:node <2a94d88a63985c1bd5dd8459da37d19bShape>.
<86361b29e6bd88aa50ea2841449410e5time_instantShape> sh:property <2a94d88a63985c1bd5dd8459da37d19bShape>.
